{"title":"儿歌","authors":["雪地"],"dates":[{"year":1959,"month":6,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"儿歌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雪地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红太阳，正午啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树叶子，晒卷啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社员叔叔不怕热，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凤凰山前耢棉花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姨姨的脸儿晒红啦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叔叔的衣服汗透啦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叔叔姨姨歇歇吧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"树荫底下喝凉茶。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}